nodes.text: Vukorah was a human female who held the rank of general in the Unbroken Clan criminal syndicate. After the rival Mourner's Wail Syndicate bombed and killed Unbroken Clan soldiers on Chorgad, Vukorah attacked Mourner's Wail forces. Seeing the Unbroken Clan's leader to be ineffective, Vukorah eventually eliminated those with loyalties to the old line, becoming the leader of the syndicate.
